Venizelos Says Greek Crisis Opportunity to Overhaul Economy

-- B y   M a r c u s   B e n s a s s o n
-- 
2011-10-07T10:21:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/venizelos-says-greek-crisis-opportunity-to-overhaul-economy.html
Greek Finance Minister Evangelos Venizelos said the crisis affecting  Greece  was an opportunity to
overhaul the economy and draw more foreign investment.  “Greece is in a critical and difficult period but the
crisis is also an opportunity to change the economy,” Venizelos
told reporters in  Athens  today after a meeting with German
Economy Minister Philipp Roesler.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marcus Bensasson in Athens at 
